 Umar reported: A man asked the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhich places are worst?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cI will not know until I ask Gabriel.\u201d Then he asked Gabriel, and he said, \u201cI will not know until I ask Michael.\u201d Michael came, and he said, \u201cThe\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2016,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/28\/hereafter-faith-eventually-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25645,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Whoever has faith eventually enters Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel, upon him be peace, came to me to give the good news that anyone from my nation who dies without associating partners with Allah will eventually enter Paradise.\u201d I said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41733,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/01\/15\/salaf-on-nifaq-companions-fear-they-will-become-hypocrites\/","url_meta":{"origin":25645,"position":5},"title":"Salaf on Nifaq: Companions fear they will become hypocrites","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bukhari reported: Ibn Abi Mulaykah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI met thirty companions of the